{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Putni mettahs? Nahzeet / fa-\npulzinajtees wiſſi Swehri Lau-\nkā/ nahzeet un ehdeet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Dauds Ganni irr mannu\nWiḫna-Dahrsu mattajſchi / tee\nirr mannu Tihrumu faminnu-\nſchi/ mannu iſwebletu Tihrumu\nirr tee darrijſchi par tukſhu poh-\nstu Weetu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſſch irr pohſta dar-\nrihts/ ta pohſta Weeta preckſch\nmanntin behdajahs/ wiſſa Sem-\nme irr pohſita/ ka neweens irr/\nfas to ar Sirdi wehra jemus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſſas angſtas Tuksne-\ntes Weetas irr Pohstitajt nah-\ntutchi/ jo ta KUNGA Sohbirs\naprihj no weena Semmes Balka\nkihdj ohtrains/ un Meers ne irr\nne kahdai Meeſat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee fehj Kweefchus/ bet\nEhrſchkus winat plaus/ tee\nganu gzuhti strahda/ bet nenee-\nka pehn / tapehz tohpeet Kannā\njuhfu Augtu deht/ un tahs kar-\nſtas Bahrsibas ta KUNGA\nDeht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta fakta tas KUNGS\nprett wiſſeem manneem nikneem\nKaimizceem / kas mannu ee-\nmantojamu Teefu aiskarr/ ko es\nmanneem Ifraēta Gaudim lizzis\necmantoht: Reds/ es aiſgrabb-\nſchu tohs no winno Semmes /\nbet to Namnu Juhda aiſgrabb-\nschu es no winno Widdus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pehz ka es tohs eſmu\naiſgrabbis/ tad es atgreeſitchobs/\nun patr tecni apschchloschebs/ es\natweediſchu tohs atpakkat / ik-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "katru pee fawa Ihpachuma/ u-\nikkatru uhs fawu Semint.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ja tee manno Lau-\nſebu Zeltu tikkučhi mahzifees\nun swehrehs pee mannu Wah-\nda/ tik teefcham ka tas KUNG-\ndſihwo/ itt ka tee mannuſ Lau-\ndis irr mahzijſchi pee Bdā-\nswehreht / kad taps tee mannu\nLauſchu Widdu ustaifitti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ja tee ne klaſſibs-\ntad aiſgrahbschu es grahbti-\nscho Tautu/ un iſmihiinaschu to-\ntakta tas KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XIII. Nodalla.\nJeremijum cohp to Juudu Atmeſchana zam-\nweena Lihsibu preckſchſchmeta: 1. Tapeh-\npakuhdina wiſſch tohs pee Atgreeſchonakno-\nGrehkeem: 15/ 16. Jo Ne atgreeſchana-\nno Grehkeem irr wiſſas Iſpoſſiſchanas-\nWaina: 23.-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Da irr tas KUNGS uhs-\nEmannt fazzija: Eij/ un\npirgees weenu lumu Joh-\nſtu/ un johſees ar to ap tanveem\nGurneem/ bet ne keez to Uideni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad pirku es weenn Johſtu\npehz ta KUNGA Wahrdā/ un\navjohſohs ar to ap imanneem\nGurneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad notikte ta KUNGA\nWahrdā uhs manni ohtra Ret-\nſe/ un fazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jem to Johſtu/ ko tu effe\nprzis/ kas ap tanveem Gurneem\nirr/ un zellees/ eij pee ta Wratta/\nun aptlep to tur kahda Ak-\nmiou-Ratna Plaisuma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es qahju/ un aptlehpu\nto pee ta Wratta/ ka tas KUNGS\nman bij pawehlejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
